  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Story Background</h2><br>A disaster that could have been avoided triggered a chain reaction that nearly wiped out humanity.<br>Despite a global effort to combat the catastrophe, almost 20 years have passed, and the devastation still rages on...<br>In the city SG01, which was just recently included in the disaster relief plan,<br>\"I\" strive to maintain a \"stable\" life shared with \"her,\"<br>But the personnel allocation demands of the disaster relief plan conflict with my wishes.<br>And that's not all...<br>The series of abnormal events that began on April 9, 2074,<br>Hint at a larger conspiracy and power struggle behind everything...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Introduction</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/f5573da95c26b8ec00fc8ab9f78adfa3.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/2f1ab1a138e46f215aa73fbf02f6588b.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/4d1365d2b530263bf35aaabd0a3217e0.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/67dedf7063ec51b5c517c4650ab19b7d.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/ccd577f28f70232ff21b9bc1a66a6407.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><strong>Simple and User-Friendly UI</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/a644abe38ad8f7bdcb11e859cc2c09c3.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>The game includes features such as option recall and dialogue skip.<br><br><strong>Multiple Branching Paths</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/4c7d18502277c905344dfcaab2465dcd.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>The demo has three different endings based on branch choices (excluding bad endings).<br><br><strong>Collectible Text Information</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/32832983355b8175fd38a6b19d073fbc.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>You can instantly view collected text information within the game.<br><br><strong>Rich Sci-Fi Settings</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/2752d9dd15f8394726abbf62def70248.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>In addition to the fictional sci-fi elements, some real-world scientific knowledge is also involved.<br><br><strong>Join our QQ group to get early access to related information</strong><br>QQ group: <strong>690971277</strong>",
